<title>THE BANNER OF THE CROSS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal puonlap zak dinga piek I hitau ie,
 Lalpen sepaihte kiengah;
 Sepaih bangin tu'n puonlap chuh I zak ui,
 Tatsate banga la sa'n.

[V2]
 Masuon un, Masuon un!
 Krista'h bangkim channa'n ngai un;
 Lalpen chawihat na'n la sau uo,
 Kross puonlap lim nuoi achun.

[V3]
 2. Tui kinawk bangin melma lauhum mahleh,
 I puonlap khaisang hitiu;
 A lim nuoiah Lal sepaih I hih ziek un,
 Thudik mang galzam puoi tiu.

[V4]
 3. Gam leh tuipi chung mihiem chenna cheng ah,
 Chanchin Pha thu phuongzak un;
 Lal thisan bek puonlap chanchin chuh genun,
 Lalpen sepaihte I hiu.

[V5]
 4. Zing khawvak lopi hungtun nang a nai tai,
 Nicheng in a nai deuh deuh;
 Lalpen masang ah melma chuh tawm tan au,
 Kross-in khawvel nuoisieh ding.</lyrics>
</song>